vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 52 “Administrative Provisions for the Construction Codes," of the Dallas City Code, Sections 102.3, 302.1, and 303.9.2; and adding a new Subchapter 13, to (1) add the definition and the authority to establish a Private Provider model; (2) allow expiration of incomplete permit applications; and (3) provide an exception for refunds related to void permits due to limitation of time under Section 302.1.2. - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
